race.comment: Competitive finale. LASTAR (4) was a winner fresh then fifth on the Parks track at Morphettville last time. Has been beaten for speed lately but over this trip and off the low draw will sit closer and stalk the pace. Looks well placed here and weighted to feature. COME ALONG JEFFREY (2) was safely held last time but the start prior finished seventh but not far from the winner in tougher company. Speedy type who will take catching. ICE SYMPHONY (3) has a wide gate but the ability to feature. The run two back was good enough for this. OUTPOST (6) is a last start winner and will take catching again.
